pipelines.description: Newly uploaded patchsets enter this pipeline to receive an initial +/-1 Verified vote from Jenkins. This is used for TripleO patchsets only so that if the TripleO cloud suffers a failure, folk looking can tell that there isn't a system infra problem. only a TripleO specific problem. Once the TripleO test cloud is multi region and has some months of proven stability this will be folded back into the normal check pipeline.
pipelines.name: check-tripleo

pipelines.description: On-demand pipeline for requesting a run against a tripleo experimental jobs - slower and running without redundancy - so not yet gating. Leave review comment of "check experimental" to run jobs in this pipeline.
pipelines.name: experimental-tripleo

pipelines.description: Each time a change merges, this pipeline verifies that all open changes on the same project are still mergeable.
pipelines.name: merge-check
